           The IDA Pro Disassembler and Debugger is an
           interactive, programmable, extendible, muti-processor
           disassembler hosted on the Windows platform.
           Universally acclaimed as the best disassembler money
           can buy, IDA Pro has become the de-facto standard for
           the analysis of hostile code and is quickly
           establishing itself as a major tool in the field of
           vulnerability research.

           NOTE: During first start IDA will show you screen with
           license agreement. Since it was purchased in Russia,
           license agreement is written in Russian. If you don't
           understand Russian, just press left button ("I agree"
           on Russian) and enjoy.

           NOTE: What did we patched here?
           --- Unblacklisted key from our previous release.
           --- Patched IDA to work also with non-Russian locales
           and open all databases, not only produced with
           "Russian" version.
           --- Patched IDA to work in advanced mode although key
           is from standard version (from our previous release).
           --- Removed supplier's name from binary files. No
           watermarks were removed, but he (and we also) don't
           care.
